Description: Description: Provides tools to download, process, and analyze real-time 
    meteorological radar images from Simepar (Paraná, Brazil). Designed to support 
    the 'Rede Agropesquisa' hydrological monitoring, it includes functions to detect 
    rainfall intensity based on RGB color values within predefined circular study 
    areas. Features automated integration with the 'Telegram Bot API' 
    <https://core.telegram.org/bots/api> to send spatialized image alerts and 
    an interactive 'shiny' dashboard for easy configuration and continuous 
    weather tracking.
